"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-04-shelly-ann-fraser-price-posts-emotional-statement-shock-olympics-100m-withdrawal-21356935\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce says it is 'difficult for me to find the words to describe the depth of my disappointment' after missing out on the 100m semi-finals atParis2024 through injury.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was confusion on Saturday as the Jamaican legend was a late withdrawal from her 100m semi-final in her lastOlympics.\", \"from\": 186, \"to\": 308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 225, \"end\": 233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9996012917174365, \"rank\": 0.0003988673133407795, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The three-time gold medallist came through her heat on Friday but ahead of her semi-final on Saturday evening 'DNS' (Did Not Start) was next to Fraser-Pryce's name.\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 421, \"end\": 424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Domain_Name_System\", \"score\": 0.9999123466569294, \"rank\": 8.726168178637714e-05, \"text\": \"DNS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Domain_Name_System\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Domain_Name_System\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was some confusion as to why, but Jamaica's team manager, Ludlow Watts, later revealed that she had withdrawn due to injury, saying: 'When we got the news she was warming up and so it came as a surprise to me.\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 516, \"end\": 523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999993171969, \"rank\": 6.82574462649212e-10, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 540, \"end\": 546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ludlow\", \"score\": 0.9999999965082225, \"rank\": 3.4918728639340046e-09, \"text\": \"Ludlow\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ludlow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ludlow\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We only got the information that she is injured, but doctor Warren Blake is addressing the matter and we will speak further on the matter.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warren_bioregion\", \"score\": 0.9999999727276648, \"rank\": 1.3328490973846598e-08, \"text\": \"Warren\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warren_bioregion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warren_bioregion\"}, {\"begin\": 759, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\", \"score\": 0.8179615157142831, \"rank\": 0.22255140379055544, \"text\": \"Blake\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This was a surprise and disappointment because the whole world would love to see Shelly in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 914, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_South_Park_families\", \"score\": 0.9896280156624527, \"rank\": 0.00776039183594917, \"text\": \"Shelly\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_South_Park_families\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_South_Park_families\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Apart from being a Jamaican, I am sure that people who love track and field would be very disappointed globally.'\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-old, who is the most decorated 100m sprinter of all time, has since reacted to the crushing news, thanking fans for their support over her epic career.\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1216, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It is difficult for me to find the words to describe the depth of my disappointment,'Fraser-Pryce wrote on social media.\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1339, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I know that my supporters share and shoulder this disappointment with me.\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am truly blessed to have had the steadfast support of my fans since my Olympic debut in 2008.\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The support of my fans, my country, and the larger community has rooted me in immense gratitude that has sustained me throughout my career.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'With every step and win, you all have been there for me.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My faith has always affirmed my trust in my journey.\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for continuing to be with me today and every day.'\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"St Lucia's Julien Alfred went on to win 100m gold, saying: 'I have dreamt of this day I am just it happy it happened.\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1828, \"end\": 1836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"score\": 0.9999958758483904, \"rank\": 4.122578005923781e-06, \"text\": \"St Lucia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I thank god for bringing me through for me giving me that strength to come so far.\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It means a lot to them (St Lucia).\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2057, \"end\": 2065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"score\": 0.9999958758483904, \"rank\": 4.122578005923781e-06, \"text\": \"St Lucia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so happy it (gold medal) came.'\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fraser-Pryce is still scheduled to run in the 4x100m, but clearly that will depend on whether she has recovered from injury.\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2230, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Second known sex offender at the Olympics exposed after being hired by China  ArrowMORE:Andy Murray enjoying retirement as he scoffs doughnut in Paris crowd with fellow tennis legend  ArrowMORE:Why USA star Freddie Crittenden strolled to 110m hurdles last place on purpose  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2435, \"end\": 2440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9874162663425037, \"rank\": 0.012269252704331136, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\